518
00:37:06,950 --> 00:37:07,880
Aku tak tahu.

519
00:37:10,870 --> 00:37:12,080
Dia aneh.

520
00:37:26,910 --> 00:37:27,880
Guru Su.

521
00:37:30,630 --> 00:37:31,480
Begini,

522
00:37:31,950 --> 00:37:32,830
minggu depan

523
00:37:32,910 --> 00:37:34,320
Guru Zheng akan kembali mengajar.

524
00:37:34,760 --> 00:37:36,240
Entah kenapa dia mempersingkat

525
00:37:36,320 --> 00:37:37,430
cuti melahirkannya.

526
00:37:38,760 --> 00:37:39,760
Jadi...

527
00:37:40,800 --> 00:37:43,000
Jadi, terima kasih atas bantuanmu
beberapa waktu ini.

528
00:37:45,950 --> 00:37:47,910
Baik, aku mengerti.

529
00:37:48,910 --> 00:37:50,590
Terima kasih banyak sudah menjadi

530
00:37:50,670 --> 00:37:51,630
guru pengganti.

531
00:37:52,390 --> 00:37:53,630
Anak-anak sangat menyukaimu.

532
00:37:55,600 --> 00:37:56,440
Jangan sungkan.

533
00:37:58,950 --> 00:37:59,840
Guru Li.

534
00:38:02,390 --> 00:38:03,430
Guru Sang

535
00:38:03,760 --> 00:38:04,710
hari ini belum datang?

536
00:38:05,800 --> 00:38:06,720
Wu Yan

537
00:38:07,040 --> 00:38:07,920
izin cuti kepadaku.

538
00:38:08,010 --> 00:38:09,330
