539
00:38:09,630 --> 00:38:11,470
Kenapa? Ada keperluan?

540
00:38:13,910 --> 00:38:14,920
Tidak.

541
00:38:15,840 --> 00:38:16,720
Aku pergi dulu.

542
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:27,080
[Departemen Teknik]

543
00:38:25,080 --> 00:38:26,640
Aku sangat penasaran.

544
00:38:26,720 --> 00:38:28,600
Kalian yang bertanggung jawab
atas berita ini.

545
00:38:29,560 --> 00:38:30,480
Sang Wu Yan.

546
00:38:31,160 --> 00:38:32,600
Kenapa kau seolah tak ada hubungannya?

547
00:38:33,600 --> 00:38:35,320
Xu Qian merekam pejalan kaki.

548
00:38:35,400 --> 00:38:36,440
- Apa kau tahu?
- Aku...

549
00:38:38,360 --> 00:38:39,430
Ini bukan masalah besar.

550
00:38:39,520 --> 00:38:41,040
Kurasa tanpa bagian ini

551
