juga tidak apa-apa.

552
00:38:42,360 --> 00:38:44,000
Kalian berusaha keras
membuat begitu banyak.

553
00:38:44,080 --> 00:38:45,760
Pemirsa hanya mendengar sekilas saja.

554
00:38:45,840 --> 00:38:47,280
- Sikap apa ini?
- Kenapa bilang begitu?

555
00:38:47,800 --> 00:38:48,640
Aku...

556
00:38:54,840 --> 00:38:56,000
Lakukan wawancara ulang.

557
00:38:56,080 --> 00:38:56,880
Sebelum Jumat,

558
00:38:56,960 --> 00:38:57,960
harus dapat materinya.

559
00:38:58,040 --> 00:38:59,760
Kalian tak punya kesempatan lain lagi.

560
00:39:05,520 --> 00:39:06,360
- Terima kasih.
- Terima kasih.

561
00:39:16,470 --> 00:39:18,670
